        .container-fluid.w-100.text-center(style='padding-top:0px;padding-bottom:10px; color: white')
          .card-deck
            .card(style="background-color:black;")
              .card-body.text-left
                p.mb-0
                  i.fas.fa-question-circle.mb-0(style='margin-right: 8px')
                  | Go to <a href='https://developer.amazon.com/alexa' target="_blank">developer.amazon.com/alexa</a> and log in.
        .container-fluid.w-100.text-center(style='padding-top:0px;padding-bottom:10px; color: white')
          .card-deck
            .card(style="background-color:black;")
              .card-body.text-left
                p.mb-0
                  i.fas.fa-question-circle.mb-0(style='margin-right: 8px')
